                        <div class="viewport">
                            <div style="top: 0px;" class="overview">

                                <div class="regular">
                                    <p class="font-size-12 text-align-adjust-small">
                                        Intelleges’ provides a simple, streamlined platform for companies to collect, store
                        and share compliance information securely.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="font-size-12 text-align-adjust-small">
                                        In recent years, corporations who manage and operate large global supplier and customer
                        ecosystems have been forced to understand, develop, collect and report on increasing
                        amounts of regulatory data about these third parties to the jurisdictions in which
                        they do business. Regulations surrounding protocols such as physical and information
                        security; privacy and confidentiality; and small business/diversity continue to
                        proliferate. They are particularly onerous for firms that do business under contracts
                        with governmental authorities and/or in countries that are of security concern.
                        This problem will worsen as companies become more global, competition increases
                        and economic powers seek to level the playing field for international trade.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="font-size-12 text-align-adjust-small">
                                        Compliance data collection requirements exceed the scope of traditional Supply Chain
                        Management (SCM), ERP, CRM or GRC systems. Consequently, in even the largest firms,
                        third party compliance is a largely manual, time consuming and cumbersome effort.
                        For each app licable regulation, teams are typically assembled to understand regulations
                        and produce questionnaires, which are manually distributed across a network of tens
                        of thousands of suppliers and customers and whose responses are then summarized
                        and collated, usually through Microsoft Excel, into reports. The current process,
                        in most companies, bears significant time, cost and reputation risk.
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="font-size-12 text-align-adjust-small">
                                        Working with large government contractors, Intelleges has developed a web-based,
                        cloud solution which provides:
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="font-size-12 text-align-adjust-small">
                                    </p>
